    "title": "Ilaya Thalapathy Vijay Welfare Association",
    "description": "The journey of our leader was not laid out with flowers. He turned obstacles into stepping stones and marched forward with determination.\\nHis life stands as a story of success. Since 1992, his supporters have been defined by their commitment to social service. What began as a gathering of admirers naturally evolved into a fan movement. He then transformed it into a service organization, and ultimately into a people\u2019s movement - a true testament to his leadership. He introduced a flag for the movement and gave it a powerful call: \u201cWork! Rise! You Can!\u201d - a vision that continues to inspire and lead the way."
  },
