    "title": "A Helping Hand in Times of Crisis - Kerala Floods & Pandemic Relief",
    "description": "During the devastating COVID-19 pandemic in 2020, our leader contributed \u20b91.3 crore as relief support, standing firmly with the people in a time of global crisis. When Kerala was affected by floods, he extended immediate assistance by sending relief materials in truckloads, reaching those affected in their hour of need."
