    "title": "Vetri Kolgai Thiruvizha - A Historic First State Conference",
    "description": "On October 27, 2024, in Vikravandi, Villupuram district, a massive conference titled \u201cVetri Kolgai Thiruvizha\u201d was held, drawing participation from over 1.5 million people. At this first state conference, our leader unveiled the movement\u2019s five core ideological leaders, sending a powerful message across all directions. Tamilaga Vetri Kazhagam stands as the only political party in Tamil Nadu to declare women as ideological leaders - marking a bold and historic step in political representation"
  },
