    "title": "Parandur Protest - A Leader Who Rose as the Voice of the People",
    "description": "Stepping into the field against the Parandur airport issue - which threatens water bodies, agricultural lands, and farming communities - our leader stood firmly with the people. When he came to meet his own people, countless obstacles were placed in his path. Yet, rising above every barrier, he became the voice of the voiceless - and continues to echo their concerns."
